div.div: 更新 CustomChatWindow 组件，优化界面交互和事件处理

Add MessageDelegate, TelegramChatWindow, and TelegramSearchBox components
- Implemented MessageDelegate for custom message rendering in chat. - Created TelegramChatWindow for managing chat interface with a splitter layout. - Developed TelegramSearchBox with custom styling and search functionality. - Integrated context menu actions for chat items including pinning, muting, and marking as read. - Added support for dynamic chat data generation for testing purposes.

Refactor BorderlessWindow implementation and UI components
- Introduced a new BorderlessWindow class with a modernized design and functionality. - Removed the old form.ui file and replaced it with a programmatic UI setup in main.cpp. - Enhanced the MainArea and StandardTitleBar classes for better layout and styling. - Implemented a new title bar button design with hover effects and modern styling. - Added support for resizing the window by dragging edges and corners. - Updated the minimize button to follow a modern Fluent Design style. - Removed deprecated FramelessWindow class and associated files. - Improved event handling for window state changes and mouse interactions. - Cleaned up the CMakeLists.txt to reflect the new project structure.
